{"tid":1493171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"829 Winter On Fire 遍地開花放映會","createTime":"2019-08-21T06:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T18:41:32.000Z","uid":308898,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"551fd57a2dcea85c50af366a7c969aa77d2ac55d","tid":1493171,"uid":308898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"大家好，相信大家都可能睇過Winter On Fire 呢套有關烏克蘭在2013年的紀錄片。套戲令我感覺到，反送中運動正在重複著烏克蘭的歷史，亦帶俾我好多思考。我好希望更多香港人能夠睇到呢部片，所以我在攪緊一個829 Winter On Fire 遍地開花放映會<br />\n<br />\n成件事我只是做發起人，負責吹雞。咁大家一起約在829 去播Winter On Fire, 但我不會參與任何運作，所以係真正冇大台，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n由於Winter On Fire 只在Netflix 平台播放，故此有好多人可能末必有機會看到。但此片對於反送中運動，甚有啓蒙意義。希望多些人看後能對運動有更多了解及思考。特別是一眾和理非。最後能夠有映後討論，幫助大家思考。<br />\n<br />\n829 Winter On Fire 遍地開花放映會：<br />\n<br />\n暫時表示會考慮放映的地區包括：大埔 / 西貢 / 嶼南 /元朗 / 青衣 / 港島西 / 港島西/油麻地 / 九龍灣 / 沙田 / 大圍 / 天水圍 / 牛頭角 / 旺角 / 港島東/大坑or灣仔/深水埗/土瓜灣/將軍澳 （不斷更新中）<br />\n<br />\n我希望能夠有更多單位參與放映，有興趣加入成為放映單位，可以 message TG @rothman250<br />\n<br />\n記住：<br />\n各區自己要有人有 Netflix Account，時間地點形式全部由你去定，唯一一個條件是829播放<br />\n真正冇大台, 自己搞<br />\n但我哋可以搵人做聯合文宣"},{"pid":"316c24abb8fb5eb59772a778067ab1407a27b3cf","tid":1493171,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"版權問題?"},{"pid":"5214e0a0201c60e4e459c95cf480e8903ed47ce1","tid":1493171,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c6/ASerbianFilm_UK.jpg/195px-ASerbianFilm_UK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc6%2FASerbianFilm_UK.jpg%2F195px-ASerbianFilm_UK.jpg&h=02a9d8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一部塞爾維亞電影"},{"pid":"f35476da435208c415d8e56ade2308cbe8beacd8","tid":1493171,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:51:13.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86e1f8cccd5791bec0c8eb3ea8d82774562e90a4","tid":1493171,"uid":162581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60feaf2e76237187877dc93e6cc96537beef7aa5","tid":1493171,"uid":162581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:24:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"727db884012c885cef065fc7364c906f82f983a8","tid":1493171,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e47cac7d3df6fb1cba1ee64ca621ae93ba87cb35","tid":1493171,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"d9fc9cf703546e08f00842b11559922ddd8e5e62","tid":1493171,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c3d21ebad17e6b6da691b36560e3e8992554dc81","tid":1493171,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"c4d416b65859a1053f3059216708d3d230bf0611","tid":1493171,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"7afa53ef4611e7664400dff746d92bd1d9bda857","tid":1493171,"uid":174936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38bb7ca7dd6b8a503652e784717