咁出名<br />\n關於警隊權力腐化既片竟然冇人提<br />\n<br />\n另外提議雙螢幕<br />\nA螢幕播全集<br />\nB螢幕播5分鐘濃縮版<br />\n畢竟路過既人只會願意留10分鐘 <br />\n應該問自己點樣憑呢十分鐘打動路人"},{"pid":"72b51f3876a3d2257361e519d9f4fd5a2358b730","tid":1493171,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0884e994b31eb38f68fab65014b7d3abde8b99db","tid":1493171,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"會去"},{"pid":"328607944516a058f1df4108c88336110f403147","tid":1493171,"uid":59800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}